						<div class="postbody">It takes about half the screen time to update one nametable using a not-unrolled loop.  This is for a simple memcpy style update.
<br />
<br />In my scroller demo, it took about 5 frames to update an entire nametable when I used the same code called when scrolling rows onto the screen.  Your mileage may vary.</div>

					
